    "description": "角色設計是以課堂上練習人物臉型、骨架、姿勢與服裝造型為練習基礎，輔以動漫畫產品觀察與解析，配合環境與設定描述，讓學生學習人物設計之技能與知識。<br><br>Role design is to use the classroom to practice face-shaped and structure and posture and Costume styling as a basis for practice, Supplemented by animation and comics observation and analysis, Match the environment and configuration description, Enable students to learn the skills and knowledge of character design.<br>",
    "prerequisites": "需先修習並通過「素描類」或「繪畫類」或「表現技法類」之手繪基礎課程",
